What shame to us such a conjecture
<lb/>on their part, and how deadly to
<lb/>discipline. You see then, whither,
<lb/>prompted by duty and <add facs="#img_647_z002" rend="no-caret _HMp" place="above" hand="#HM" change="#StFa">the</add> law I steadfastly
<lb/>drive. But I beeseech you, my
<lb/>friends, do not take me amiss. I
<lb/> feel <del facs="#img_647_z006" rend="single-stroke _ink1" hand="#HM" change="#StFa">even</del> <metamark facs="#img_647_z005" rend="#HM _inkG" place="inline" function="caret" change="#StFa">^</metamark> <del facs="#img_647_z007" rend="multi-stroke _HMp" hand="#HM" change="#StFa"><add facs="#img_647_z007" rend="caret _ink1" place="above" hand="#HM" change="#StFa">much</add></del> as you do for this
<lb/>unfortunate boy. But did he know
<lb/>our hearts, I take him to be of
<lb/>that generous nature that he
<lb/>would feel even for us on whom
<lb/>in this military necessity so
<lb/>heavy a compulsion is laid.
</ab></div></body></text>